{
  "id": "6a461cce6721e7e676cb3a59",
  "title": "inajob-with-ai",
  "created": 1782979793,
  "updated": 1783699736,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a461cce6721e7e676cb3a59",
      "text": "inajob-with-ai",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979793,
      "updated": 1782979793
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461cd00000000000c858d7",
      "text": " https://inajob-with-ai.pages.dev/",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979793,
      "updated": 1782979818
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461ce90000000000c858d9",
      "text": " [inajob.icon]の日記を[grasp]で[OpenCode]に読み込ませて、Wikiのような構造を再構成させる取り組み",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979818,
      "updated": 1782979869
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d210000000000c858da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979874,
      "updated": 1782979874
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5118f80000000000d42e20",
      "text": "\tテキストデータ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699705,
      "updated": 1783699710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5118fd0000000000d42e22",
      "text": "\t\t[https://github.com/inajob/inajob-with-ai GitHub - inajob/inajob-with-ai · GitHub]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699710,
      "updated": 1783699713
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5119000000000000d42e23",
      "text": "  \tMarkdownのような感じだが、リンクが`[]`になっている点に注意（出来ればどこかで直したい）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699713,
      "updated": 1783699736
    },
    {
      "id": "6a5118f80000000000d42e21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699705,
      "updated": 1783699705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d2a0000000000c858db",
      "text": " 対話のログは気が向いたらlogs以下に書き出してる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979882,
      "updated": 1782979904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d4d0000000000c858dc",
      "text": " ページの作り方のパターン",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979918,
      "updated": 1782979928
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d580000000000c858dd",
      "text": "  〇〇について分析して → ページに書き出して",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979928,
      "updated": 1782979940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d640000000000c858de",
      "text": "  〇〇と、☓☓について関係性を分析して → ページに書き出して",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979940,
      "updated": 1782979971
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d830000000000c858df",
      "text": "  〇〇について、分析するために必要な質問をページに書き出して",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979971,
      "updated": 1782979991
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461d9a0000000000c858e0",
      "text": "   ページに[inajob.icon]が答えを書き込む",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782979995,
      "updated": 1782980068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a461de30000000000c858e1",
      "text": "   再度読み込んで、分析を進めてもらい、ページを作る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782980068,
      "updated": 1782980082
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4628470000000000c858e2",
      "text": " [KarpathyのLLM Wiki]と関係がありそうだが、よくわかってない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782982728,
      "updated": 1782982801
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b807c0000000000fa911d",
      "text": " OpenCodeの1つのセッションでダラダラ会話して随時ページを更新してもらってる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783332989,
      "updated": 1783333013
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b80960000000000fa911e",
      "text": "  コンパクションもどんどん起きる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783333015,
      "updated": 1783333022
    },
    {
      "id": "6a46284c0000000000c858e3",
      "text": " 2026/07/03",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782982732,
      "updated": 1783075207
    },
    {
      "id": "6a47918a00000000004c3b95",
      "text": "  もう100ページいった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783075211,
      "updated": 1783075220
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49d6ee0000000000aefa5d",
      "text": " 2026/07/05",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783224046,
      "updated": 1783224059
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49d6fb0000000000aefa5e",
      "text": "  明朝体にした",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783224060,
      "updated": 1783224064
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49d7030000000000aefa5f",
      "text": "  グラフをつけてみた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783224068,
      "updated": 1783224073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49d7090000000000aefa60",
      "text": "   あまり意味はない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783224073,
      "updated": 1783224077
    },
    {
      "id": "6a47917f00000000004c3b94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783075200,
      "updated": 1783075200
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f0390000000000ee9e55",
      "text": "\t面白い[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230523,
      "updated": 1783230525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f03b0000000000ee9e57",
      "text": "\t\t自分も同世代かつ状況が似てるからか、興味あるトピックが多い",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230525,
      "updated": 1783230849
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f08b0000000000ee9e58",
      "text": "\t\t交通整理できるの強くていいなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230605,
      "updated": 1783230610
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f0e60000000000ee9e59",
      "text": "\t\t[根本的な保守性 - inajob with ai https://inajob-with-ai.pages.dev/#/%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AA%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E6%80%A7]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230696,
      "updated": 1783230710
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f0e60000000000ee9e5a",
      "text": "\t\t\t取り入れたさ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230696,
      "updated": 1783230713
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f0f70000000000ee9e5b",
      "text": "\t\t\t自分は思考で冒険したことを外に出しちゃう（挑んじゃう）のがたぶん良くない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230713,
      "updated": 1783230732
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f10b0000000000ee9e5c",
      "text": "\t\t\t冒険は思考まで、はバランス良さそう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230732,
      "updated": 1783230759
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f1350000000000ee9e5d",
      "text": "\tプロンプトも気になる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230776,
      "updated": 1783230781
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f13b0000000000ee9e5e",
      "text": "\t\tAIにつくらせると文章が小難しく＆長くなりがちだけど、これ含めて[inajob.icon]さんのはなんかすごく端的でわかりやすい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230781,
      "updated": 1783231142
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f1530000000000ee9e60",
      "text": "\t\tプロンプトなのか、ログがそうなのかはわからない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1783230805,
      "updated": 1783230814
    },
    {
      "id": "6a49f14c0000000000ee9e5f",
      "text": "  [OpenCode]の[Big Pickle]です[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783230798,
      "updated": 1783333229
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b81710000000000fa9120",
      "text": "   Buildモードで会話してる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783333234,
      "updated": 1783333245
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b81990000000000fa9121",
      "text": "  元が箇条書きベースのページだからそれに倣ってるのかも[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783333274,
      "updated": 1783333292
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b81510000000000fa911f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783333202,
      "updated": 1783333202
    }
  ]
}